{"description":"\nBy default, the RadioInput component is a custom styled HTML radio button.\n\nAdjust the size of the RadioInput and its label text via the `size` prop. The default size is\n`medium`. See [RadioInputGroup](/RadioInputGroup) for more details\n\n```js\n---\ntype: example\n---\n<InstUISettingsProvider>\n<Flex>\n  <Flex direction=\"column\" margin=\"medium\" gap=\"medium\">\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"small\"\n      value=\"foo\"\n      name=\"bar\"\n      size=\"small\"\n    />\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"medium\"\n      value=\"foo2\"\n      name=\"bar2\"\n    />\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"large\"\n      value=\"foo3\"\n      name=\"bar3\"\n      size=\"large\"\n    />\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"large disabled\"\n      value=\"foo4\"\n      name=\"bar4\"\n      size=\"large\"\n      disabled\n    />\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"large readonly\"\n      value=\"foo5\"\n      name=\"bar5\"\n      size=\"large\"\n      readOnly\n    />\n  </Flex>\n  <Flex direction=\"column\" margin=\"medium\" gap=\"medium\">\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"small\"\n      value=\"foo6\"\n      name=\"bar6\"\n      checked\n      size=\"small\"\n      checked\n    />\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"medium\"\n      value=\"foo7\"\n      name=\"bar7\"\n      checked\n    />\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"large\"\n      value=\"foo8\"\n      name=\"bar8\"\n      size=\"large\"\n      checked\n    />\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"large disabled checked\"\n      value=\"foo9\"\n      name=\"bar9\"\n      size=\"large\"\n      disabled\n      checked\n    />\n    <RadioInput\n      label=\"large readonly\"\n      value=\"foo10\"\n      name=\"bar10\"\n      size=\"large\"\n      readOnly\n      checked\n    />\n  </Flex>\n</Flex>\n</InstUISettingsProvider>\n```\n\n### Guidelines\n\n```js\n---\ntype: embed\n---\n<Guidelines>\n  <Figure recommendation=\"yes\" title=\"Do\">\n    <Figure.Item>Use sentence-style capitalization</Figure.Item>\n    <Figure.Item>Use a clear and concise label for RadioInput</Figure.Item>\n    <Figure.Item>Optionally include a heading to provide further clarity</Figure.Item>\n  </Figure>\n  <Figure recommendation=\"no\" title=\"Don't\">\n    <Figure.Item>Have a single RadioInput</Figure.Item>\n    <Figure.Item>Use long labels for RadioInput</Figure.Item>\n    <Figure.Item>Display more than two radio inputs horizontally</Figure.Item>\n  </Figure>\n</Guidelines>\n```\n","displayName":"RadioInput","methods":[{"name":"focus","docblock":null,"modifiers":[],"params":[],"returns":null},{"name":"focused","docblock":null,"modifiers":["get"],"params":[],"returns":null},{"name":"checked","docblock":null,"modifiers":["get"],"params":[],"returns":null},{"name":"id","docblock":null,"modifiers":["get"],"params":[],"returns":null}],"props":{"label":{"required":true,"tsType":{"name":"ReactReactNode","raw":"React.ReactNode"},"description":"The label displayed next to the checkbox"},"value":{"required":false,"tsType":{"name":"union","raw":"string | number","elements":[{"name":"string"},{"name":"number"}]},"description":"This maps to the low level HTML attribute\n[with the same name](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/radio#value)"},"id":{"required":false,"tsType":{"name":"string"},"description":"The id of the input element. If not provided, a unique id will be generated."},"name":{"required":false,"tsType":{"name":"string"},"description":"The [name](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/radio#defining_a_radio_group)\ndefines which group it belongs to, it's managed by the `RadioInputGroup`\nthis component belongs to.\n\nDo not set it manually."},"checked":{"required":false,"tsType":{"name":"boolean"},"description":"Sets the `checked` prop of the underlying input element. If left undefined,\nthe component will control its own state."},"disabled":{"required":false,"tsType":{"name":"boolean"},"description":"Whether to disable the input"},"readOnly":{"required":f